You have to make sure that you have all the required tools installed and cofigured properly (as decsribed at the begining of the page), as well as the enviroment variables

I used Genymotion emulator as a plugin to Eclipse

Follow the steps starting from 'Build the Project':
http://cordova.apache.org/docs/en/4.0.0/guide_platforms_android_index.md.html


The created apk will be located at SMART-GH-Android->platforms->android->ant-build->CordovaApp-release-unsigned.apk